track_notes: This is the shorter path up and down from Calla Melosa to reach Cime de Marta. First walk on the small path to refugio Monte Grai (no more valid as Sota) then walk on the forest road (easy)
If you are fit enought you can activate these 2 summits.Nothing difficult; you can short-cut but also use the forest road all the way.
Nice walk, long but no difficult. you can park at La Baisse de Gereon; plenty room on summit for antenna.
